<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.4">
<l>vaḷḷalē matucūtaṉā veṉmarakata malaiyē yuṉainiṉain</l>
<l>teḷka ṟanta ventā yuṉṉai yeṅṅaṉam viṭukēṉ</l>
<l>veḷḷamē purai niṉpukaḻ kuṭaintāṭip pāṭik kaḷittu kantukan</l>
<l>tuḷḷa nōyka ḷellān turantuyntu pōntiruntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O generous man, Madhusūdana, my emerald mountain, our father</l>
<l>who gives [me] thinking of you [and] slighting(?), how would I leave you,</l>
<l>diving into your fame that is like a flood [and] dancing, singing being exulted, rejoicing, rejoicing,</l>
<l>driving away all the pains that are there, escaping completely(?).</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
